snippet.textDisplay:
To,
you
I see you have liked this song.
This is not the end.
Although this is a good reinterpretation of the original(to certain extent) but the one my musarrat nazeer is and shall always remain the original benchmark.
Yes, there will be good songs, bad songs and as i have already said this is not the end.
Coke studio is a good way to get younger generation to get introduced to old melodies but they are not the end. There is no need to compare them with originals.

And for God sake stop postin *who is here after coke studio*.
